  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지, 박스는</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4abf6162-e357-45a4-8a86-4d47898a27b7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-4abf6162-e357-45a4-8a86-4d47898a27b7\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTRfMTg4/MDAxNzUyNDg1MTMwNjA0.hZHU-03WlAx3ifl4y8ee-k6shJWlN9fVfI-SmUsd2d4g.rV7WnyjUpa4LPhhNGEEjTy-gQKaQYDMRrnOKABUtN3og.PNG/SE-4abf6162-e357-45a4-8a86-4d47898a27b7.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTRfMTg4/MDAxNzUyNDg1MTMwNjA0.hZHU-03WlAx3ifl4y8ee-k6shJWlN9fVfI-SmUsd2d4g.rV7WnyjUpa4LPhhNGEEjTy-gQKaQYDMRrnOKABUtN3og.PNG/SE-4abf6162-e357-45a4-8a86-4d47898a27b7.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">내부 종이 패드</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-93c9d4a9-816d-454f-90ca-e178e8f90348\" style=\"color:#555555;\">내부 종이 패드나 시끼리(?)를 만드는 것이 중요한 상자들이 있습니다. 이런 상자들은 제품의 내용물을 담거나 파손 위험으로부터 보호하는데 그 목적이 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95b479a6-ffc5-44d3-ac8f-d06038724835\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-baa27353-711d-477c-8443-1b2595e8248b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-95baf9c9-ccda-48ab-a6d4-6a2b9d082866\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e49b8d41-30bf-45b2-bff3-1fa29b84d183\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 패드는 종이로 제작할 수도 있고 스티로폼, 스펀지로 제작이 가능하고 또는 플라스틱, 나무로도 제작이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-fbffc6d8-06b6-4f58-b1f2-b824d64090ea\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-fbffc6d8-06b6-4f58-b1f2-b824d64090ea\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTRfMTAx/MDAxNzUyNDg1NDQ4MTQ0.ZkxNhZhNfevI7DY2xlZwiZl-RJInMrFCykrQPKZYpccg.QmReT4FvEh1PLgr5VJ6jAXzIvgvblZL4t196yoanbdUg.PNG/SE-fbffc6d8-06b6-4f58-b1f2-b824d64090ea.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTRfMTAx/MDAxNzUyNDg1NDQ4MTQ0.ZkxNhZhNfevI7DY2xlZwiZl-RJInMrFCykrQPKZYpccg.QmReT4FvEh1PLgr5VJ6jAXzIvgvblZL4t196yoanbdUg.PNG/SE-fbffc6d8-06b6-4f58-b1f2-b824d64090ea.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0fb82362-52b8-4f64-a68c-04d36e6dbac0\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aefcac8c-3856-47f4-bb45-888e1184526d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-8fa23ed8-068b-435a-964f-1e675a062901\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 모양의 패드를 만들려면 일단 제품이 나와 있어야 하고 제품을 보고 정확한 상담을 통해 제작이 가능합니다. 제품의 크기와 끼워봤을 때의 안전성이나 내구성 등을 고려하려면 여러 번의 목형 수정을 통해 패드는 완성됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d8c2ef7b-ff97-460e-a3a0-2bae13d04678\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ed96c9fb-2e4b-4ca6-ab4b-40751d87e0f2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-163048cb-35b4-49f1-8b61-ad1f9384fc47\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a624749d-f071-4f62-9524-7bc8dc980825\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이런 과정을 거치기 때문에 기본적으로는 납기 시간이 많이 소요되며 납기를 촉박하게 잡으면 반드시 사고가 날 수 있기 때문에 납기는 여유 있게 잡아주시는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-50ccfe1c-afdc-47e0-9ec7-c920d4c52086\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4e01388-6866-4755-bdc5-34cd9452aafc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c89b1c57-3dcd-4958-ac2c-8377dfc4783e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4c2cde1a-3858-4de1-b4ea-e410681578d4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보통의 박스에 들어가는 패드는 일단 다음과 같은 진행과정을 거치게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a06953c-7f95-4cae-a713-70ae9d891928\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-e70c2d48-0ef9-48c1-a315-e0384567f064\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e2025c3f-6e3d-4ab5-897d-b04220ca5b9d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3d7753fa-d732-4b35-ad69-740984b7bb4e\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>구성 기획</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-18182c30-4119-48b5-a1bb-910f1102ad73\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c4dbc6cf-a20b-4ead-9959-aa683d7ba8cf\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fff8b2;\">여러분이 제품을 처음으로 출시하시거나 패키지 박스를 처음 제작하시는 것이라면 반드시 전문 패키지 회사와 상담을 통해 제품 구성 방법을 상의하시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-47f7ea57-b78e-42d2-a9a3-756a90301619\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-47f7ea57-b78e-42d2-a9a3-756a90301619\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTVfMTI4/MDAxNzUyNTM4MjMwMDY1.mCV-kEQjuZuL90kybwlZx6RCF3JvL6sl9-y4YHrkrvsg.qg4zwpvxJmUXlvTmB3SchhsFEfC-LbpOO1eEoS1iD7og.PNG/%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_%ED%8C%A8%EB%93%9C_%EC%8D%B8%EB%84%A4%EC%9D%BC001.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTVfMTI4/MDAxNzUyNTM4MjMwMDY1.mCV-kEQjuZuL90kybwlZx6RCF3JvL6sl9-y4YHrkrvsg.qg4zwpvxJmUXlvTmB3SchhsFEfC-LbpOO1eEoS1iD7og.PNG/%EB%8B%A8%EC%83%81%EC%9E%90_%ED%8C%A8%EB%93%9C_%EC%8D%B8%EB%84%A4%EC%9D%BC001.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5f3bb11f-7c65-416b-970c-8d965e09c230\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49681ae4-7d36-4f8d-abc5-5cd4e7c850da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-3efa5f90-3a23-404a-ab9c-0238b2455666\" style=\"color:#555555;\">어떤 방법으로 어떻게 제작할지는 전문가와 상의하고 결정하는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-10afe9fb-f21d-4b0a-9658-701bd8d21d7a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-92ceba40-380a-4bce-9e81-140c976f7cfe\" style=\"color:#555555;\">들어가는 내용의 제품이 다양하거나 많을 경우 여러 가지 방법을 고려하여 제작하는 것이 효과적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-395924df-5bc7-4eab-a934-252ca165897e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-395924df-5bc7-4eab-a934-252ca165897e\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTVfNTUg/MDAxNzUyNTM4NDA5OTc2.waBou7BLdYIVcd7XWZA4Kp2MvdOsm4EBQdvukSi0018g.fl59mTed-yWVFcH8I7c9zZcpVE2O16FQjeMImGmkbVog.PNG/SE-395924df-5bc7-4eab-a934-252ca165897e.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"595\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTVfNTUg/MDAxNzUyNTM4NDA5OTc2.waBou7BLdY